n, Selexipag, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/162143/', '[1] "Product Information. Xarelto (rivaroxaban)." Bayer Inc, Toronto, IA.[2] Hooks MA "Tacrolimus, a new immunosuppressant--a review of the literature." Ann Pharmacother 28 (1994): 501-11[3] "Product Information. Prograf (tacrolimus)." Fujisawa, Deerfield, IL.', 1767369485);
